# Harness-only knobs for the @eval tier (opt-in live-crew model evaluation).
# Copy to .env (git-ignored) and fill in. Never commit real keys.
# Required fitting-out for the @eval tier; assume present. A missing key is
# incomplete fitting-out (a Captain blocker), never a silent skip.

HARNESS_OPENROUTER_API_KEY=
HARNESS_EVAL_MODEL=deepseek/deepseek-v4-flash
# HARNESS_EVAL_PROVIDER=openrouter
# HARNESS_EVAL_TIMEOUT_MS=600000
